Original Implementation
-----------------------
This library was extracted from the CLPIC (Common Lisp P2P Intellectual Property
Chain) project. The bridge protocols implement cross-chain communication patterns
based on established blockchain interoperability standards.

Cryptographic Algorithms
------------------------
- SHA-256: FIPS 180-4 (NIST)
  Pure Common Lisp implementation with no external dependencies.

Cross-Chain Standards
---------------------
- IBC (Inter-Blockchain Communication): Cosmos network standard
- Light Client Protocols: Ethereum 2.0 Altair, Tendermint/CometBFT
- Merkle Proofs: Standard binary Merkle tree verification
- HTLC (Hash Time-Locked Contracts): Atomic swap pattern

